import JAVAFX_GENERATOR from "../../images/password-generator-screenshot.jpg"

export const javaFxProject = {
    id: "first-website",
    header: "JavaFx Password Generator",
    img: JAVAFX_GENERATOR,
    imgHeight: "500px",
    imgWidth: "1100px",
    videoHeader: "Video Demonstration",
    summary: "The point of this project was to test my UI development skills. It is a password generator, with a few settings that I can toggle to tailor the password that is generated to my liking.",
